source.name: NSF Graduate Research Fellowship Program Award Recipients, 2003
source.description: NSF's Graduate Research Fellowship Program (GRFP) provides three years of support for graduate study leading to research-based masters or doctoral degrees in disciplines relevant to the mission of the Foundation. This dataset includes GRFP award recipients for 2003.
